      "comment": "ARCHIE'S GIFT (1) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from four starts. Below best last time at Geelong (23.03) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5, finishing a 3 length fourth. Looks suited here and rates on top. KRAKEN MILLY (2) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (24.43) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Shepparton. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. OLYMPIA ONYX (6) has been out of the placings the last couple but was a T3 RSTW winner (28.48) three back at this track. Can turn it around this time. BLAME KARISSA (8) has strong claims after a top-three finish last time out.",
